      <title>日本表示，日元跌至 34 年来新低，不排除采取任何外汇行动</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/japan-says-it-wont-rule-out-any-fx-action-yen-hits-34-year-low-2024-04-11/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本财务大臣铃木俊一周四表示，在美元兑日元汇率飙升至34年来的高点后，当局不排除采取任何措施应对汇率过度波动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/japan-says-it-wont-rule-out-any-fx-action-yen-hits-34-year-low-2024-04-11/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 03:00:29 GMT</pubDate>
